{
  "texts": [
    "Let C ← {{s 1 },..., {s n }}.",
    "For each cluster C ∈ C, store its union mask M (C). 2.",
    "For clusters C i, C j, define the cost of merging C j into C i asϕ(C i, C j) = m(C i ∪ C j) -m(C i) = M (C i) ∪ M (C j) ∪ M ({s, s ′ }) -m(C i),where s ∈ C i and s ′ ∈ C j are arbitrarily chosen. 3.",
    "Greedy merge.",
    "Repeatedly select(C p, C q) = arg min i̸ =j ϕ(C i, C j),breaking ties by minimum m(C i)."
  ]
}